_sText:
- 2015 remake of the map "mg_huge_tv-tower_v1" made in 2009.
- Added 3D skybox / lots of entities / fancy colors.
- 64 spawns (32 CT spawns and 32 T spawns) 
- 2 Elevators. 
- The tower has 4 floors. 
- ladders protection (to prevent jump glitch) 

Credit:

- Xylon - Maker/Tester.
- The original maker of the map mg_tv-tower_beta for the map idea.
- TopHATTwaffle for the 3D skybox prefab.
